==English==

===Etymology===
[[sea]] + [[urchin]] (meaning [[hedgehog]]), due to the similarity in appearance to the hedgehog.

===Noun===
'''[[sea]] [[urchin]]'''

# A marine [[animal]] with a hard, round body covered with spikes.

